# File-level variables (shared across all requests)
@base_url = https://httpbin.org
@timeout = 30

### GET request with file variables
GET {{base_url}}/get?timeout={{timeout}}

### POST with request-level variables
@user_id = 123
@user_name = John Doe
POST {{base_url}}/post
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "user_id": "{{user_id}}",
  "name": "{{user_name}}",
  "timeout": {{timeout}}
}

### Variable priority test
@host = request-level.com
GET https://{{host}}/anything
